lyrics.text:
‘Oku kumi ‘e he ‘Eiki ‘a e fānau ma’ana;
‘Oku taau kinautolu ke fai ha lakanga;
Pea tu’u ‘ene tohi ‘a homou hingoa,
‘A e koloa kānokato ‘a e ‘Eiki Sihova.

Faka’amu ‘e he ‘Eiki he ma’u pe kei si’i;
Kei lelei pē ‘a e loto, te’eki ‘uli’i;
Pea tu’u ‘ene tohi ‘a homou hingoa,
‘A e koloa kānokato ‘a e ‘Eiki Sihova.
